The unusual fish is a quest item used in Sigmund the Merchant section of the The Fremennik Trials quest. It is obtained by giving a sea fishing map to the fisherman in Rellekka. The fish can then be given to Skulgrimen in exchange for a custom bowstring.

It is obtained by giving a [[sea fishing map]] to the fisherman in [[Rellekka]]. The fish can then be given to [[Skulgrimen]] in exchange for a [[custom bowstring]].
